      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need to talk to someone about something weird. i think i'm seeing things before they actually happen. like, i saw this specific cracked coffee mug at a cafe this morning and it felt... heavy? like it was vibrating with something. then i saw the news and there was a huge pileup on the highway near that same street right after. i'm starting to think i'm not seeing time the way everyone else does. it's like the future leaves traces on objects. does that make any sense??",
