      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The concept of \"temporal residue\" or objects holding future energy falls outside of established mainstream science. From a scientific perspective, all observations of the physical world are currently understood through linear time and known laws of physics. However, if you are feeling a tangible, physical sensation linked to these events, it might be worth exploring how intense anticipation or pattern recognition can manifest physically. Consulting a neurologist or therapist could help investigate if there are any physiological explanations for the chest sensations you are experiencing.",
